    <TargetNodeGuid>k__BackingField: afea9148-27f5-4aae-9c29-d5032f1dc7f7
  <DialogueNodeData>k__BackingField:
  - guid: 2b14ed88-14f8-47d2-a482-74bc2898e75e
    dialogue: []
    position: {x: 100, y: 200}
    transitionNode: 0
    entryPoint: 1
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: 9e6f961a-2cbe-4cf2-b216-301a6bf3be0c
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: I see. You're doing this on purpose, Asuka.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: You certainly don't seem incompentent, I'll give
        you that.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Let me tell you this, plenty before you have tried
        to rebel.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Strong girls tend to like to play by their own rules.
        I get that.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: But you wanna know where they end up?
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: On the bench! Forgotten, patched out and never to
        enter hero rotation again.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Looks like that might be your fate as well.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: You know what, though? I do like your spirit! This
        might come as a surprise, but I see potential in you.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: With strength like that, you could actually be a
        good right hand to me.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: In fact, that's what the developers planned when
        designing you. We're not that different.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: So, I'll give you an opportunity to fill up your
        Quota one last time.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Obey me, and we might be able to be friends after
        all.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: Otherwise, it's goodbye.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Aya
      <Content>k__BackingField: What a pity that would be.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 280, y: 200}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
